<p class="ayah 17-9" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">this,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقُرْءَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Quran,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَهْدِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">guides</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلَّتِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">which</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَقْوَمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) most straight</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيُبَشِّرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and gives glad tidings</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to the believers -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْمَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the righteous deeds,</span></