<p class="ayah 17-14" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱقْرَأْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Read</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كِتَـٰبَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your record.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَفَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Sufficient</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِنَفْسِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) yourself</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْيَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">today,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">against you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَسِيبًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as) accountant."</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/17:14" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="2043"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>14<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
