<p class="ayah 17-68" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَفَأَمِنتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Do you then feel secure</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that (not)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَخْسِفَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He will cause to swallow</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَانِبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">side</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْبَرِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the land</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُرْسِلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">send</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">against you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَاصِبًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a storm of stones?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><