<p class="ayah 17-107" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامِنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِۦٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُؤْمِنُوٓاْ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوتُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">were given</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعِلْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the knowledge</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن قَبْلِهِۦٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">before it,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranTex